import React from 'react'

import '../styles/Home.css'

const About = () => {
    return (
        <Grid container direction="column">
            <Grid item>
                <Navbar/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item container>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} >
                    About B.B.
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                <Footer/>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    )
}

export default About
